date: Sun Feb 13 2022 12:02:27 GMT+1100 (Australian Eastern Daylight Time)
description: Kylie Minogue has splashed out $8 million for a mansion in Melbourne's eastern suburbs. The 53-year-old negotiated a private sale at the end of last year. The four-bedroom home is close to her sister Dannii in Hawthorn East and the siblings parents in Canterbury. The prestige property features three bathrooms, elegant living areas and an alfresco dining area with an outdoor kitchen.
